description: Lovely two bed with parking! This top floor corner unit is one of only a couple units in the building that has its own private entrance from the street. Open kitchen with breakfast bar and gas cooking. Huge windows and high ceilings throughout the unit let the light pour in. Two big bedrooms with the primary having a large walk in closet. There is common laundry but there are laundry hook ups in the unit for you to install your own machines. Great storage within the unit, plus a private storage closet, outdoor deck and one off street parking space come with this condo. Close to everything in the most rapidly gentrifying area of Southie, like Tatte and the T! This is a great unit for a first time home buyer. Unit has tenants until August 31, 2025.
